    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless shape\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and even still has that new-car smell inside. You really won't find another one this clean out there. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
