      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, boasting its original, deep-luster factory paint protected by a fresh ceramic coating. The interior is absolutely pristine, featuring supple leather with no visible wear on the bolsters and a cabin that still retains its original scent. Every electronic component, from the tactile dash buttons to the premium sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it has been strictly garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. With zero imperfections, no history of accidents, and a spotless undercarriage, this is an investment-grade example ready for a discerning collector.",
